# Sound Files for Stewardship5

Place the following audio files in this directory:

- `lobby-music.mp3` - Upbeat Kahoot-style loop music for the lobby
- `tick.mp3` - Short tick sound for countdown timer
- `submitted.mp3` - Success chime when a player submits their answer
- `reveal.mp3` - Fanfare for results reveal
- `countdown.mp3` - Countdown beep sequence

Note: Audio files are optional. The app will work without them.
